title: Necdet Darıcıoğlu
text: Necdet Darıcıoğlu (May 4, 1926 in <a href="Antalya">Antalya</a>, <a href="Turkey">Turkey</a> – September 14, 2016, <a href="Ankara">Ankara</a>) was a <a href="Turkish%20people">Turkish</a> <a href="judge">judge</a>. He was president of the <a href="Constitutional%20Court%20of%20Turkey">Constitutional Court of Turkey</a> from March 2, 1990 until May 4, 1991.
